ao1.name: Compliment Messages for who you just met
content: Your style is incredible—it really suits you.
You have the most captivating eyes I’ve ever seen.
I really admire how confident you are—it’s inspiring.
You carry yourself so gracefully; it’s impossible not to notice.

ao2.name: Playful and Flirty Messages
content: Do you always have this much charm, or is it just me?
I think meeting you might have been the highlight of my day.
So, are you always this amazing, or did I catch you on a good day?
I was trying to focus, but then I remembered our conversation and got distracted.

ao3.name: Thoughtful Messages
content: What’s one thing you’re really passionate about? I’d love to know.
I noticed how kind you were to [someone]. That really stood out to me.
What’s something you’ve always wanted to try but haven’t yet?
You seem like someone who’s full of amazing stories. I can’t wait to hear more.
What’s the best advice you’ve ever received? You seem like someone who gives great advice.
